VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'scaffolding the thing. Then it will set up different artifact types like one for docs and one for signal which covers things like feedback, idea, observation, as well as tickets. This also log to MD file which at beginning is empty. And then I create this kind domain/support'

[18:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'folder. As I mentioned, for each loop I found it really useful if I would define a contract that is capturing the goal of the loop, the overall workflow and boundaries, and outstanding task list'

[18:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
